name.ja: スネークアイ・ワイトバーチ

text.en: If you control a FIRE monster, you can Special Summon this card (from your hand). You can only Special Summon "Snake-Eye Wight Birch" once per turn this way. During your opponent's turn (Quick Effect): You can send this card and 1 other face-up card you control to the GY; Special Summon 1 "Snake-Eye" monster from your hand or Deck, except "Snake-Eye Wight Birch". You can only use this effect of "Snake-Eye Wight Birch" once per turn.
